node.text: Watch the lap where the #FerrariSF90Stradale Assetto Fiorano goes beyond imagination to set a new production car lap record at Indianapolis Motor Speedway as part of #FerrariRacingDays.

node.text:
Swipe for this weekend’s annual #FerrariRacingDays celebration and for a glimpse of the 100+ racing Ferraris in attendance at the historic Indianapolis Motor Speedway.⁣
⁣
Cover photo: Drivers took part in a unique oval-lapping session on the famed oval layout. In the traditional three abreast formation, all of the drivers participating in the weekend took their turn for a few laps around the same pavement used by the drivers of the Indianapolis 500. ⁣
⁣
#Ferrari #Motorsports #IndianapolisMotorSpeedway
